
Secure Instant Messaging System (Server)
========================================

To compile the server, run
  * `make build` or
  * `javac -cp ../libs/json-simple-1.1.1.jar:../libs/commons-io.jar: \
      ../libs/commons-codec.jar:../encrypt/ ./Server.java`

To run the server, run
  * `make server` or
  * `java -cp ../libs/json-simple-1.1.1.jar:../libs/commons-io.jar: \
      ../libs/commons-codec.jar:../encrypt/ Server <port>`



Dependencies
------------

This program requires several libraries:
  * json-simple
  * commons-io
  * commons-codec

And uses the APIs provided by:
  * ../encrypt/Crypt.java

And this program depends on maintaining keyfiles in the ./ directory.
The keys were generated by the encryption APIs provided by ./encrypt/:
